displayName.text: Citi Bike: Pike St & Monroe St

originalText.text: This is an absolutely genius and fairly inexpensive for use. I think they cost $12 a day or $24 for 3 day or something close to that. The only catch is you have to dock them at a station every 30 minutes or you will be charged extra for every 15 minutes after that until you actually do dock. Google maps provides the locations for each docking station and actually shows how many spots are available. Really awesome for people visiting to save money.
